description:
Minecraft modded. In this Minecraft episode we check out some of the new NPC behavior in our town. Then we build a drilling machine and start setting up a fishing shack.

Mod List: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10h_y5lmGSB675LM55wm22VaLWqV70YepsLyBAxEmd6Q/edit#gid=0
Note: I did not compile this list and it is not entirely up to date. I'll try compile an official list (and hopefully the pack) when I find some time.
